org.glassfish.contextpropagation

Interface ContextViewFactory


  • public interface ContextViewFactory
    Use this factory to provide support for a custom ViewCapable class. The createInstance method is invoked through the a ContextMap's createViewCapable method and as needed when decoding incoming propagation contexts.
